ing: 0px; list-style: outside none none; border: 0px; color: rgb(100, 100, 100); font-family: \"Noto Sans\", sans-serif, dotum, gulim;'> </p>\n<p style='font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: outside none none; border: 0px; color: rgb(100, 100, 100); font-family: \"Noto Sans\", sans-serif, dotum, gulim;'><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14pt;\">● ​발표평가 : 2026. 5. 14.(목)</span></span></p>\n<p style='font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: outside none none; border: 0px; color: rgb(100, 100, 100); font-family: \"Noto Sans\", sans-serif, dotum, gulim;'> </p>\n<p style='font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: outside none none; border: 0px; color: rgb(100, 100, 100); font-family: \"Noto Sans\", sans-serif, dotum, gulim;'><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14pt;\">  * 결과 발표 : 5월 중 예정</span></span></p>\n<p style='font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: outside none none; border: 0px; color: rgb(100, 100, 100); font-family: \"Noto Sans\", sans-serif, dotum, gulim;'><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14pt;\">   (자세한 일정은 첨부파일 참조)</span></span></p>\n<p style='font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: outside none none; border: 0px; color: rgb(100, 100, 100); font-family: \"Noto Sans\", sans-serif, dotum, gulim;'><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14pt;\"> </span></span></p>\n<p style='font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: outside none none; border: 0px; color: rgb(100, 100, 100); font-family: \"Noto Sans\", sans-serif, dotum, gulim;'> </p>\n<p style='font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: outside none none; border: 0px; color: rgb(100, 100, 100); font-family: \"Noto Sans\", sans-serif, dotum, gulim;'><strong><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: